videos.description: TCU's Alex Robinson lobs an alley-oop pass to Kevin Samuel for the slam before halftime vs. Eastern Michigan.
videos.headline: TCU's Samuel slams down alley-oop

videos.description: TCU's Jaylen Fisher drives and tosses an alley-oop to Kevin Samuel for a two-handed dunk in the second half.
videos.headline: Fisher lobs to Samuel for TCU dunk
